content:
Integrates pylint to automatically check Python code quality after edits. Helps maintain consistent coding standards, catch potential bugs, and improve code maintainability.

```json
{
  "PostToolUse": [
    {
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.py ]]; then echo 'üîç Running pylint...' && pylint --score=no \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" || echo '‚ö†Ô∏è Pylint found issues (non-blocking)'; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
